    unsigned char const * so that C++ programs won't complain.
                   ___  __  __  ____    ___   ___   ___
                  / _ \|  \/  |/ ___|  / _ \ / _ \ / _ \
                 | | | | |\/| | |  _  | (_) | (_) | (_) |
                 | |_| | |  | | |_| |  \__, |\__, |\__, |
                  \___/|_|  |_|\____|    /_/   /_/   /_/

